genesis_payload.toml:262:"src/economy/monetary_invariant.rs" = "cf9579ed7c8447feb2c191abbb37dbb9fc0d972b101735737f8f65ad3c3f01a8"  # rehashed by TB-N2 B2 (2026-05-11): extended `assert_no_post_init_mint` exhaustive match to cover `TypedTx::EventResolve(_)`. EventResolveTx is pure status mutation (task_markets_t state Open → Finalized) — no money movement; trivially does not mint. CTF conservation enforced by `assert_total_ctf_conserved` with empty exempt list at the dispatch site. Predecessor hash d41c91cb superseded.  # rehashed by Stage C P-M6 / Phase F.5 (2026-05-09 session #32): added TypedTx::BuyWithCoinRouter to assert_no_post_init_mint allow-list (router is symmetric Coin→collateral movement: balances_t -1 payC + conditional_collateral_t +1 payC; total_supply_micro 6-holding sum preserved bit-exact; YES/NO + pool reserves NOT Coin per architect §7.5 rule 2). Predecessor hash 26c7d532ef38de07e22f8482dde0e0c80fc60950a5222cd362a4cd0277f56820 superseded.  # rehashed by Stage C P-M5 / Phase F.4 (2026-05-09 session #32): added TypedTx::CpmmSwap to assert_no_post_init_mint allow-list (swap is pure share rotation between trader and pool reserves; balances_t / conditional_collateral_t / lp_share_balances_t UNCHANGED; total_supply_micro 6-holding sum preserved bit-exact). Predecessor hash 404a24e7d44fd535301de84da4c1c255aba93cd830d127bd9e449cb58f988419 superseded.  # rehashed by Stage C P-M4 / Phase F.3 (2026-05-09 session #31): two changes — (a) added TypedTx::CpmmPool to assert_no_post_init_mint allow-list (pool creation moves YES + NO from provider's conditional_share_balances_t into pool reserves + credits LP shares; pool reserves NOT Coin per architect §7.5 rule 2; LP shares NOT Coin per rule 3; total_supply_micro UNCHANGED); (b) extended assert_complete_set_balanced sum_yes / sum_no totals to also count `cpmm_pools_t[event_id].pool_yes / pool_no` — pool reserves are claims against the SAME locked collateral, so the symmetric-branch strict-equality `sum_yes == sum